- If you do not want to run the tests in hot mode you can run the command:

    ng test --no watch

- The true value of testing is in the fact that when someone fucks with your code you can tell by looking at what tests pass and fail.




SMART/CONTAINER COMPONENT
=========================

- Is a component that normally gets its data from services and not from inputs.
- The Home Component in this course is a good example of a smart components.